    "media:imagetext": "Next time,\nfly First Class or\nAmbassador Class on us.\nJoin TWA's Frequent Flight Bonus Program and\nafter just one flight, you'll receive a free one-class\nupgrade certificate good on any TWA® domestic\nflight, valid for six months from date of issue. So,\nafter receiving your certificate, you can enjoy the\nluxury and comfort of First Class or Ambassador\nClass® service on your next TWA flight within the\nU.S. There's more in store once you've joined the\nFFB® program, including:\n• Free travel within the continental U.S. at 20,000\nmiles\n• Europe or the Middle East at 35,000 miles\n• Free upgrades for TWA Gold and Silver Card\nholders*\n• Miles that have no expiration date\n• 3,000 bonus miles after your first TWA flight as an\nFFB member, too.\nJoin today! For instant enrollment,\ncall (800) 221-2000 in the U.S.\nOutside the U.S., call your local TWA office.\n*Upgrades are subject to availability of unreserved seats.\nPurchase of a qualifying ticket required.\nPlease allow 2-3 weeks for delivery of your membership\nmaterials, which explain all rules and conditions for par-\nticipation in the program. TWA FFB program rules, special\noffers, blackout dates, awards and mileage levels are sub-\nject to change without notice. TWA reserves the right\nto terminate the FFB program or portions thereof at\nany time.\nTWA\nFREQUENT FLIGHT BONUS PROGRAM",
